{# templates/report.md.j2 — gate-operator overview.

   Renders ``_REPORT.md`` into the replica root. Every extraction
   gets its own section; every item gets its own sub-section
   with the materialization marker on the first line followed
   by a full field dump (no truncation).

   Inputs:
     basename       — source basename
     topic          — classify topic string
     quintet        — classify quintet object
     summary        — extract-summary's text (verbatim)

     extractions    — { kind: {items: [
                          {display_name, materialized, fields: [
                              {name, value}, ...
                          ]},
                          ...
                       ]} }
                       Pre-formatted by build_report — every field
                       value is already a Markdown-safe string.

     synthesis_paths       — list of ``21 WIKI/<slug>.md`` paths
     orphan_links          — wikilink targets unresolved at
                             prune-replica time.

     manifest_modifications  — [{vault_path, kind, name}] for atomic
                               pages that overwrite an existing
                               vault page (manifest entries with
                               op=modified).
     synthesis_modifications — [{vault_path, name}] for synthesis
                               pages whose path already exists in
                               the vault and would be overwritten.
#}
